      "uco-core:description": "Cyber-espionage threat actor active since at least 2012; attributed by Talos with high confidence via exclusive use of the Sagerunex backdoor, consistent victimology, and TTPs. UCO has no dedicated ThreatActor class, so the group is modeled as an Organization.",
