      ],
      "uco-core:name": "Lateral movement via WMI/Impacket",
      "uco-core:description": "Actor used Impacket (and WMI, per the attack-chain diagram) to execute remote processes and commands and move laterally across the internal network toward a data-exfiltrating host.",
